Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:57.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}終わらないメロディーを歌いだしました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:05.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とても大好きで　少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}でも　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:13.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}止まることができなくて嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:22.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:27.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:33.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:38.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}同じにはできないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:50.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心も　未来も　笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:57.11,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そう　まだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:00.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:04.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:08.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:10.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:14.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:18.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You see what I want tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:28.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠と 儚さと 震える夜もあるけれど
