Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:57.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}吟唱出漫无止境的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:05.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}实在过于喜欢 同时伴随些许痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:13.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}由于无法停止已经开始厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:22.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便在重要的你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:33.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}收入眼底的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:38.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可能尽然相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:50.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论心意 未来还是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:57.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}对 还有素未谋面的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:10.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:28.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}虽然会有永恒和如烟以及孤单的夜晚
